      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DONNA MAREE (7) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish half a length back in second (22.74) at this track in a Mix 3/4 over 401m. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Can measure up this time. FANTASIA QUEEN (8) turned spotting a big start finishing fifth (18.72) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including six wins. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Can do much better this time. MEPUNGA SHINE (4) goes very well here starting six times for two wins and three minors. Hit the frame latest (17.81) when second at Richmond Straight in a Mix 1/2/3. Can feature with the right run. CRIMSON DYNAMO (6) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
